'''双环总门'''（學名：{{lang|la|Bigyra}}）是[[不等鞭毛類|不等鞭毛類]]之下的一個子类群<ref name="pmid19213601">{{cite journal |vauthors=Riisberg I, Orr RJ, Kluge R |title=Seven gene phylogeny of heterokonts |journal=Protist |volume=160 |issue=2 |pages=191–204 |date=May 2009 |pmid=19213601 |doi=10.1016/j.protis.2008.11.004 |display-authors=etal}}</ref>。

==分類==
現時這個子类群可再分為三個亞門，即{{r|WoRMS}}<ref name="pmid16557340">{{cite journal |vauthors=Cavalier-Smith T, Chao EE |title=Phylogeny and megasystematics of phagotrophic heterokonts (kingdom Chromista) |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-molecular-evolution_2006-04_62_4/page/388 |journal=J. Mol. Evol. |volume=62 |issue=4 |pages=388–420 |date=April 2006 |pmid=16557340 |doi=10.1007/s00239-004-0353-8}}</ref>：
* Subphylum {{tsl|en|Bicosoecia}}
** Class [[Bicoecea|Bicoecea]]
*** Subclass [[Bicosidia|Bicosidia]]
*** Subclass {{tsl|es|Placididea|Placididia|Placididia}}
* Subphylum {{tsl|en|Opalozoa}}
* Subphylum [[Sagenista|Sagenista]]

而過往本分類單元分為：{{tsl|en|Blastocystis|芽囊原虫纲}}（{{tsl|en|Blastocystis}}）及{{tsl|en|Labyrinthulida}}<ref name="pmid19213601" />。

